text: GraphPad Prism software version 7 was used to analyze the experimental results. The results are expressed as scatter plots in which the mean is indicated by a line. The differences between groups were compared using an unpaired Mann-Whitney test. P < 0.05 was considered significant, and the p-values are expressed as follows: * p < 0.05, * * p < 0.01, * * * p < 0.005, and * * * * p < 0.001.
